\c 4
\s Pauro anoparidza Jesu Kristu nemoyo wose
\p
\v 1 Naizvozvo zvatine shumiro iyi, sezvatakagamuchira tsitsi, hatineti;
\v 2 asi takarasa zvinhu zvakavanzika zvechinyadzo, tisingafambi neunyengeri, kana kuminamisa Shoko raMwari; asi nekuratidza chokwadi, tichizvipupurira kuhana yose yevanhu pamberi paMwari.
\v 3 Zvinowo kana evhangeri yedu yakafukidzwa, yakafukidzwa kune avo vanoparara;
\v 4 kwavari mwari wenyika ino wavakapofumadza fungwa dzevasingatendi, kuti chiedza cheevhangeri yekubwinya yaKristu ari mufananidzo waMwari chisavhenekera kwavari.
\v 5 Nokuti hatizviparidzi, asi Kristu Jesu Ishe; uye isu \add tiri\add* varanda venyu nekuda kwaJesu.
\v 6 Nokuti Mwari wakati chiedza chivhenekere kubva parima ndiye wakavhenekera mumoyo yedu, kuti \add atipe\add* chiedza cheruzivo rwekubwinya kwaMwari pachiso chaJesu Kristu.
\v 7 Asi tine fuma iyi mumidziyo yevhu, kuti ukuru ukuru hwesimba hwuve hwaMwari, uye hwusabva kwatiri;
\v 8 \add tino\add*dzvanyidzirwa pamativi ose, asi ha\add ti\add*manikidzwi; \add tino\add*vhiringidzika, asi hatipererwi;
\v 9 \add tino\add*shushwa, asi kwete kusiiwa; \add tino\add*wisirwa pasi, asi kwete kuparadzwa;
\v 10 tichipota takatakura nguva dzose kufa kwaIshe Jesu mumuviri, kuti upenyuwo hwaJesu hwuratidzwe mumuviri wedu.
\v 11 Nokuti isu tinorarama tinogara tichipiwa kurufu nekuda kwaJesu, kuti upenyuwo hwaJesu hwuratidzwe munyama yedu inofa.
\v 12 Saizvozvo rufu rwunobata matiri, asi upenyu mamuri.
\v 13 Zvino tine mweya iwoyu werutendo, sezvazvakanyorwa \add zvichinzi\add*: Ndakatenda, naizvozvo ndakataura; isuwo tinotenda, naizvozvowo tinotaura;
\v 14 tichiziva kuti iye wakamutsa Ishe Jesu, achatimutsawo isu naJesu, agotikumikidza pamwe nemwi.
\v 15 Nokuti zvinhu zvese \add zvinoitwa\add* nekuda kwenyu, kuti nyasha dzakapamhidzirwa nekuda kwekuvonga kwevazhinji, dziwedzerwe dzive rukudzo rwaMwari.
\s Kutambudzika kwepano panyika ndekwenguva duku
\p
\v 16 Naizvozvo hatineti, asi kana munhu wedu wekunze achiparadzwa, zvakadaro wemukati unovandudzwa zuva nezuva.
\v 17 Nokuti dambudziko redu rakareruka riripo kwechinguva chiduku, rinotiitira uremu hwekubwinya kukurusisa kusingaperi;
\v 18 tisingatariri zvinoonekwa, asi zvisingaonekwi; nokuti zvinoonekwa ndezvenguva, asi zvisingaonekwi ndezvekusingaperi.
